divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking my dog out.. I always look at the sky. I thought it was a star or venus at first. Then it turned and got much bigger. Then the lights started radiating from the middle of it ut blue and white like sunrays. Then it sucked the lights back in..maybe 15 seconds later it did the same thing. It looked like a prism...I watched it for a while and then I called my neighbor to come out and see it...she told me it was a galaxy and went back in. I toom some pictures with my phone and went back in.,..I just looked form it snd it is gone.I felt awesome watching it.
